body: "## Context\nActual .agents/pm/ contains: checkpoints/, chores/, decisions/, epics/, extensions/, features/, history/, issues/, locks/, milestones/, plans/, runtime/, schema/, search/, settings.json, stories/, tasks/.\n\nDocs/ARCHITECTURE.md (lines 82-99) shows only the older subset, missing plans/, stories/, schema/, checkpoints/, runtime/.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- docs/ARCHITECTURE.md storage layout section lists all current .agents/pm/ subdirectories\n- Each new directory has a one-line description of its contents\n- CI docs-links gate stays green after the change\n\n## Evidence\ndocs/ARCHITECTURE.md lines 82-99; ls .agents/pm/ output"
